WorMotel lifespan Heritability

Tim C.

5/17/2018

This code uses processed survival data from Chris Fang-Yens lab to calcualte heritability of survival traits. The data were collected with WorMotel in spring 2018 by Matt Churgin at UPenn. Two independent bleaches of 12 strains were run on three replicate wormmotels (20 nematodes / strain). Heritability is calculated

Lifespan Heritability


There is a block effect, correcting for this effect increases lifespan heritability to 0.27.
